Package it.unicam.cs.followme.util

Interface Interpreter<E>

Type Parameters:
E - Entity that execute the commands
All Known Implementing Classes:
EntityInterpreter
public interface Interpreter<E>
An Interpreter is an object that interprets a received command parsed from the handler and supplies a suitable implementation. It is possible to add more commands
